etoposide induces an autophagy-associated atp
elevation. because it is known that autophagy is induced
by multiple dna damaging agents,3,8 we repeated studies in
u251 cells using etoposide to see whether the autophagy-
associated cytoprotective atp surge was unique to tmz. as
